Class MesonetFrame

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.awt.Component
      • java.awt.Container
        • java.awt.Window
          • java.awt.Frame
            • javax.swing.JFrame
              • MesonetFrame
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible, javax.swing.RootPaneContainer, javax.swing.WindowConstants
    public class MesonetFrame
extends javax.swing.JFrame
    Class to create a GUI to accept the given input and relay the calculated information from that. This uses a Mesonet.txt file to find the given stations with the parameters inputed by the user. The user can also add a station to the given list and there is a section where the ascii values of the selected word are displayed.
    Version:
    2019-04-29
    Author:
    Hana Stevenson
